  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for research on gendered impact of growth sectors in sub-Saharan Africa&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This grant will support research to gather more data on the gender-specific sector impacts in sub-Saharan Africa, exploring how the expansion of certain growth sectors create and constrict economic opportunities for women. The data collected will inform an advocacy strategy with members and relevant financial institutions in the region to provide these actors with a better understanding of the gender implications on women&#x2019;s economic opportunities.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
